{"tid":1902159,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【手足入嚟幫手廣傳】突發 「一加二等於三」行動！！！","createTime":"2020-02-28T07:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T11:43:40.000Z","uid":167548,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"594df45c20288cefab7e0f22d025d68e4b632d22","tid":1902159,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:59:14.000Z","msg":"「一加二等於三」行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>TLDR：每一位活躍手足拉攏兩位未登記做選民嘅黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n相信好多啱啱政治覺醒嘅手足未必了解咩是比例表制嘅直選<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總而言之, 若果我地要贏建制派, 我地嘅票數比例須達到 7：3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以70％嘅票穩穩奪得至少2/3嘅議席<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信以香港活躍遊行社運嘅人數以往年2019年出反對通知書嘅遊行均有幾十萬上落, <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">希望大家可以發揮自己嘅能力集每個人嘅力量去達至2個月內催生出100萬選票！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em><span style=\"color: violet;\">「50萬已登記手足」 拉攏 「100萬未登記手足」</span></em></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，相信！信念永存！你地做得到！<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n實際行動建議：<br />\n有大量資源嘅試下自己嗰棟樓用選民登記表塞信箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黃嘅自然會填, 藍嘅自然掉鬼佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n最緊要希望各區民主派系區議員幫手「收集」「統計」再寄去選舉事務處<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: navy;\"><br />\n呢啲均是未來配票時嘅重要數據</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XWftGao.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXWftGao.png&h=ffa98bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><blockquote>元旦遊行時所噴上嘅句子。</blockquote></span>"},{"pid":"8e005d7a670a71210c805eb599951395f6b4917c","tid":1902159,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:59:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><em>講咁撚多政治理念野, 大佬夠唔夠票架/登記左選民未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同教班太監(未登記選民)做愛一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 首先要教佢地駁返條野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em></span>"},{"pid":"0fce021f565e123db01e611d945f087a0035c8e9","tid":1902159,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:00:12.000Z","msg":"總而言之, 若果我地要贏建制派, 我地嘅票數比例須達到 7：3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以70％嘅票穩穩奪得至少2/3嘅議席<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n據2019年區議會選舉嘅得票分析, <br />\n<blockquote>總投票數：294萬<br />\n民主本土派：168萬<br />\n建制派(+中間派)：124萬<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n目標是比例達至7：3<br />\n假設建制派票數不變, 民主本土派需得到<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">額外爭取120萬票！</span></span></strong><br />\n<blockquote>公式推導：<br />\n總投票數=建制派票數&divide;0.3=413.3萬<br />\n建制派=124萬<br />\n民主派=413-124=289萬<br />\n新增票數=289-168=121萬</blockquote>"},{"pid":"48b9845e64dd0ba4a95c577cae079afdc8f5b6d2","tid":1902159,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:00:37.000Z","msg":"邊個靜靜雞負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493ae9605b206341a62de4991be43c387a84cfee","tid":1902159,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:01:00.000Z","msg":"依加都未登記嘅...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c9937525103161bc5df5ca22683422ecc07754","tid":1902159,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:01:22.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知咩是比例代表制？<br />\n<br />\n一種若選民全憑個人意願去鳩投，就會出現被對家以<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>少數票 (&lt;50%)</strong></span> 奪得<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">過半數 (&gt;50%)</span></strong> 直選議席！<br />\n<br />\n現存<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>直選框架</strong></span>下呢種制度將難以遠到<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">區選</span></strong></span>嘅Landslides。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>首先，立法會分為「功能組別」及「直選組別（採用比例代表制）」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/究竟登記做功能組別選民呢件事可以有幾麻煩/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E5%81%9A%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%B5%84%E5%88%A5%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E5%91%A2%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%BE%E9%BA%BB%E7%85%A9%2F&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJOCCrfoqRshWq79J%2FX5JLMA%3D&h=aa948992\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E5%81%9A%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%B5%84%E5%88%A5%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E5%91%A2%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%BE%E9%BA%BB%E7%85%A9%2F&h=7f7af376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/究竟登記做功能組別選民呢件事可以有幾麻煩/</a><br />\n<blockquote>我在此呼籲，如果你是功能組別選民而你又是泛民本土的，一定一定要去登記！我知道是好麻煩，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">投左都可能是建制蠃，但是你甘心咩？</span></strong>如果你有呢個身份可以登記，拜託你點都要試下！唔好衰比呢個強姦民意的正苦睇呀！！！</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/概觀民主黨-選舉機器-3-圖解選舉制度-白鴿是如何被玩殘的/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%A6%82%E8%A7%80%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8-%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%A9%9F%E5%99%A8-3-%E5%9C%96%E8%A7%A3%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6-%E7%99%BD%E9%B4%BF%E6%98%AF%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%A2%AB%E7%8E%A9%E6%AE%98%E7%9A%84%2F&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJOCCrfoqRshWq79J%2FX5JLMA%3D&h=56e84e47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%A6%82%E8%A7%80%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8-%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%A9%9F%E5%99%A8-3-%E5%9C%96%E8%A7%A3%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6-%E7%99%BD%E9%B4%BF%E6%98%AF%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%A2%AB%E7%8E%A9%E6%AE%98%E7%9A%84%2F&h=9feb12aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/概觀民主黨-選舉機器-3-圖解選舉制度-白鴿是如何被玩殘的/</a><br />\n在這種制度，計算選舉結果步驟如下：<br />\n<blockquote>一）先找出「當選基數」。「當選基數」就是 100% 除以席數。以 A 區為例，「當選基數」就是 100%/5  = 20%。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rsS0xw0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrsS0xw0.png&h=b3022089&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>二）議席按當選基數倍數分派，即 0~19%= 0 席；20~39% = 1 席；40~59% = 2 席；如此類推。<br />\n三）把總得票百分比減去已分派議席的基數，計算餘額。<br />\n四）由於 A 區有 5 個議席，而在步驟二只分了三個，因此還有兩個議席未分。它們將分給比例餘額最多的名單。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3usLJDG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3usLJDG.png&h=fe77c484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>計算完成。結果是各黨得 1 席。</strong></span>只是從多議席單票制換成比例代表制，議席分配已有這麼大的分別。<br />\n為方便讀者理解，這裡多舉一例。在這例子中，A 黨成功獲得 2 席：</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGAdSw1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGAdSw1.png&h=5bf0a797&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"385ed5b3a4e53af46d62f1358ee91649cf399226","tid":1902159,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"493ae9605b206341a62de4991be43c387a84cfee","tid":1902159,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:01:00.000Z","msg":"依加都未登記嘅...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:02:20.000Z","msg":"呢樣唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />派710億至少有300萬港豬未登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab2c0da5c9a03e1efbfb39a7e797bfd213591dc","tid":1902159,"uid":286499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:04:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d39b381987accc7a071f61